---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h1 class="text-gradient">The Biggest Challenge of My Career</h1>
      <p style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Developing OpenClaw — from concept to reality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="biggest-challenge">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="glass-panel">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="text-gradient-red">The Biggest Challenge of My Career</h2>
          <p class="experience-meta" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">OpenClaw | 2024–Present</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-2" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
          <div>
            <h3><span style="color: var(--color-accent);">01.</span> The Challenge</h3>
            <p>Developing OpenClaw has been the most complex and rewarding challenge of my career. Building an AI agent platform from the ground up required me to dive deep into uncharted territory — learning how to architect agent systems, evaluating LLMs, and creating something that genuinely creates value for users.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3><span style="color: var(--color-accent);">02.</span> The Work Involved</h3>
            <p>This challenge pushed me to develop agents from scratch, experiment with multiple LLMs to find the right fit, research emerging tech markets, design file-based structures for agent memory, master prompt engineering, implement sub-agent workflows, identify real-world use cases, and most importantly — act EARLY to leverage AI before the market saturates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--space-md);">
          <h3>Why It Matters</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #fff;">OpenClaw represents my belief that AI should be accessible and practical. By building this platform, I'm not just learning about technology — I'm creating a tool that can help small businesses and individuals harness the power of AI agents to solve real problems and create value.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
